data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_0b38b3f26d16a8d10069c2ad3eb02881978b6681f32b16dc73","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":354,"text":"TypeScript is an open-source programming language developed by Microsoft that serves as a superset of JavaScript. It introduces optional static typing and other features to enhance the development of large-scale applications. ([en.wikipedia.org](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TypeScript?utm_source=openai))\n\n**Key Features of TypeScript:**\n\n- **Static Typing:** Allows developers to define variable types, enabling early detection of type-related errors during development. ([developer.mozilla.org](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/TypeScript?utm_source=openai))\n\n- **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP):** Supports classes, interfaces, and inheritance, facilitating the creation of modular and maintainable code. ([tutorialsteacher.com](https://www.tutorialsteacher.com/typescript/typescript-overview?utm_source=openai))\n\n- **Compatibility with JavaScript:** TypeScript code is transpiled into standard JavaScript, ensuring compatibility with existing JavaScript codebases and environments. ([en.wikipedia.org](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TypeScript?utm_source=openai))\n\n- **Enhanced Tooling:** Provides features like autocompletion, refactoring support, and advanced debugging, improving developer productivity. ([typescriptlang.org](https://www.typescriptlang.org/index.html?utm_source=openai))\n\n**Getting Started with TypeScript:**\n\nTo begin using TypeScript:\n\n1. **Installation:** Install TypeScript globally using npm:\n\n   ```bash\n   npm install -g typescript\n   ```\n\n2. **Writing Code:** Create a `.ts` file and write your TypeScript code.\n\n3. **Compiling:** Compile the TypeScript file to JavaScript using the TypeScript compiler:\n\n   ```bash\n   tsc yourfile.ts\n   ```\n\n4. **Running:** Execute the generated JavaScript file using Node.js or in the browser.\n\nFor comprehensive documentation and resources, visit the official TypeScript website: ([typescriptlang.org](https://www.typescriptlang.org/index.html?utm_source=openai))\n\nFor a deeper understanding of TypeScript's design and features, you might find this presentation by Anders Hejlsberg insightful:\n\n[TypeScript: A Language for App-scale JavaScript Development](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uxFoQCM2S1k&utm_source=openai)\n "}

